Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创世之初 冥冥之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning, there was darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着一声爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量小行星撞击 从天降下死神 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Enormous asteroid impacts that rain death from the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星对撞 把世界化为尘土\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}entire planets colliding and turning worlds into dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞 上亿年间把星系的其他部分越驱越远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a black hole that's been blowing away the rest of its galaxy for 100 million years,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大质量恒星 震撼宇宙别无他求\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and massive stars that rock the universe like nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备灰飞烟灭在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Get ready to be blown away in a countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十大宇宙大爆发的倒数盘点中吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of 10 of the largest explosions in the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:01:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们全都是宇宙间的爆炸之最\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are the biggest blasts in the universe.
