Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.32,0:38:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会释放出多少能量呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}compared to our Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.03,0:38:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是惊人的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The answer is shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.46,0:38:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来到了宇宙间爆炸之最的排名第2 - 长伽玛射线暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're at number 2 in our countdown of the biggest blasts in the universe:
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.97,0:38:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是宇宙中最强大的集束能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're the most powerful concentrated beams of energy in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.31,0:38:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们在几秒乃至几分钟里所释放出的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They release many times more energy in a matter of seconds or minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.31,0:38:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数倍于我们太阳在其整个100亿年的寿命里所产生的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than our Sun will produce in its entire 10-billion-year life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.82,0:38:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们毁灭性威力的关键\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The key to their devastating power
