Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.60,0:39:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是并不厉害 因为弹丸散开了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but not that much, because the shot was spread out
