Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.94,0:39:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们的枪械专家换上长筒枪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now our firearms expert is switching to a longer barrel
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.49,0:39:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让弹丸在抵达靶子过程中 保持紧凑模式 -\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that keeps the shot concentrated in a tighter pattern as it goes downrange--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.99,0:39:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果如同伽玛射线暴那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the same effect as a gamma ray burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.84,0:39:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集束弹丸可以是毁灭性的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Concentrating the shot can be devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.05,0:39:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们庆幸的是 大多数伽玛射线暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a good thing for us that most gamma ray bursts
