Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.44,0:40:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2008年 科学家发现了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And in 2008, scientists detected
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.15,0:40:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有记录的最强大的伽玛射线暴之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of the strongest gamma ray bursts on record,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.28,0:40:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做GRB 080916c\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}known as GRB 080916c.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.66,0:40:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它持续了难以置信的23分钟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It lasted an incredible 23 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.58,0:40:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个伽玛射线暴是迄今所见过的最令人兴奋的爆发之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This GRB was one of the most exciting blasts ever seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.96,0:40:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从观察亮度及爆发的距离推断其总能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because the total power inferred from the observed brightness 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.18,0:40:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过了那时之前所有的伽玛射线暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the distance of the blast exceeded that of any other known GRB up to that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.31,0:40:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 我们可以看出高能粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Moreover, we can tell that energetic particles
