Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.16,0:41:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽玛射线暴异常强烈 粒子和辐射束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}GRBs are so powerful along the beam of particles and radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.74,0:41:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是在数千光年外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that even ones that are thousands of light-years away,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.17,0:41:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是指向我们 就会摧毁地球上的大部分生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but pointing at us, could destroy much of the life on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.30,0:41:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果说长伽玛射线暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if long gamma ray bursts
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.93,0:41:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙中最强烈的爆炸的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are the most powerful explosions in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.10,0:41:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么它们怎么能够屈居我们名录的第二号呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then how could they be number 2 on our list?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.44,0:41:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为位列榜首的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because the top spot goes to something
