Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.61,0:41:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是发生在宇宙本身诞生时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but happened when the universe itself was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.61,0:41:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排名第1 - 大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.66,0:41:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有爆炸之母\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This mother of all blasts
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.96,0:41:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格地说是膨胀而非爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is technically an expansion and not an explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.38,0:41:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它不是特定区域里的爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}since it was not a blast within a defined area.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.80,0:41:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不是发生在太空某个地方的爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It wasn't an explosion that happened somewhere in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.26,0:41:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是整个空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's all of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.80,0:42:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是时空结构本身的从无到有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the actual fabric of space-time itself coming into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.47,0:42:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此在爆炸之最的概念中 称其为大理所当然\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So in the concept of a biggest blast, it's as big as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.02,0:42:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个宇宙在爆炸中诞生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was the whole universe blasting into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.82,0:42:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爆炸的速度和温度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the speed and temperatures of the Big Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.32,0:42:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让宇宙诞生后其中所发生的一切都相形见绌了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}dwarf anything that happened inside the universe once it was formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.82,0:42:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些温度超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Those temperatures are beyond anything we can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.16,0:42:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你用常量去衡量 它们是以万亿度计的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're trillions of degrees if you measured it in the usual units,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.67,0:42:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此相对任何爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so compared to any explosions,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.88,0:42:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说 在地球上 恒星上 或者你说吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}say, here on Earth or a star or what have you,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.25,0:42:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是远远够不上的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}this is well beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.67,0:42:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究人员认为 理论上 他们可以回到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Researchers believe that, theoretically, they can go back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.01,0:42:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常接近大爆炸发生的那一刻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so close to the moment the Big Bang happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.22,0:42:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个不能再往前的那个瞬间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that a fraction of a second doesn't come anywhere close
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.43,0:42:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做时间的裁判\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to doing the time scale justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.89,0:42:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爆炸之暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The bang of the Big Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.36,0:42:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是早期宇宙所谓的大膨胀的时刻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a time in the early universe known as Inflation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.03,0:42:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙飞快扩大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The size of the universe went whoosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.99,0:43:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膨胀之快 扩大无数倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It just expanded so quickly, doubled in size many times
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.74,0:43:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在弹指一挥间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}over a very, very short interval of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.54,0:43:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种惊人的膨胀 指数般的爆扩态势\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This incredible inflationary, exponential state of expansion
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.21,0:43:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只持续了瞬间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lasted only a tiny fraction of a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.55,0:43:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百万分之   百万分之 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a millionth of a millionth of a millionth of a millionth
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.76,0:43:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百万分之   百万分之一秒钟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a millionth of a millionth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.10,0:43:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种早期膨胀中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}During this early expansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.89,0:43:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎一切都速度快过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it seemed as if things were moving faster
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.06,0:43:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱因斯坦的宇宙速度极限 - 光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than Einstein's universal speed limit, the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.23,0:43:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 膨胀之快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, it expanded so quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.40,0:43:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过了光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it was faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.40,0:43:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.36,0:43:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不违背爱因斯坦的相对论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That doesn't violate Einstein's Theory of Relativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.74,0:43:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间本身的膨胀可以快过光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Space itself can expand faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.54,0:43:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有粒子可以在空间穿行快过光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No particle can travel through space faster than the speed of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是空间本身可以也确实膨胀快过了光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but space itself can and does expand faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.18,0:44:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爆炸是最值得纪念的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the Big Bang is the largest reminder of all
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.60,0:44:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙间所有爆炸之最中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the biggest blasts in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.02,0:44:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些能量的突然释放之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}these sudden releases of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.44,0:44:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其作用远超过毁灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}do much more than destroy.
